             │(EHR, LIS, RIS, etc)│
             └────────────────────┘

HL7 Workflow:
MLLP Listener → HL7 Parser → Router → Transformer → Storage → Downstream

FHIR Workflow:
FHIR Listener → JSON Validator → Router → Transformer → Storage → Downstream



